    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed their required gradation levels for MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are accepted at Gradation 1 per MRL 2 scoping rules. The CFD hemolysis model is judged credible for identifying worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under CPB conditions, as described in the bound requirement and claim documents. No credibility gaps requiring remediation were identified.",
